{"tid":2398762,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"用左幾粒鐘睇曬 RE: Zero 動畫，不吐不快","createTime":"2021-02-07T14:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T02:19:28.000Z","uid":370062,"like":5,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9431782a25979f69f51b2f853cfe4e32bd9d91d","tid":2398762,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"睇後感如下：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 自稱宅男，熱愛動漫、電玩既男主角，竟然第一次死後，發現唔到係時光回溯？偽宅男！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 扮碇真嗣條垃圾講陌生既天花板...之後仲要講認識既天花板，以為自己好幽默，垃圾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 點解知道自己識save and load大法，唔走去老強女主角？唔make sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. Ok 你要做正人君子，咁你又走去奶腳而唔係義正嚴詞咁屌9皇帝女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 如何可以年紀係104歲但內心年齡係14歲...女主角有90年空白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 雷姆...高達先會用流星鎚好嗎？叫雷姆但有角又識暴走又會失去意識，其實你係初號機假扮既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 現代劍聖揮1劍就打爆大半間屋...重要用普通廢劍，上代劍聖點會打唔死白鯨？又係你自己話白鯨d分身好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 男主角靠自我意識送大罪司見魔女，佢又知女主角係容器候補，咁仲點可能一齊？佢點會諗唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. Save and load 大法可以用黎練功練魔法，男主角完全無諗過利用...結果比精靈騎士用木劍打到無還手之力，男主角IQ其實低過100？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10. 其實成套野，專登用個廢人男主角，再配一堆超人女友後宮，咁我不如睇韋小寶算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f83055a893bba6f5e0c82d5e74d47505dde3a4","tid":2398762,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedB